Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:02.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}becoming one with...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.66,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...the distant, glittering sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:09.58,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I read the wind, and wander away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:14.80,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}To a far off destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.30,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.60,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I fill my lungs and set off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.97,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Taking in the world's spring breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:30.23,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}While at the sun above, everyone's smiles are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.19,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}In between our hellos and goodbyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.07,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}There is only us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.70,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}We can accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.99,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The rays of the sun pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Creating a newborn sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:52.59,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The promised morning arch that we were waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.63,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}As you wave to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:02:00.43,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I decide to share with you a special day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.01,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}And our idle chatter begins.
