Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really drowsy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look drowsy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a morning person, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a morning person at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with that birdie. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tooru, that birdie keeps spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, that's just a weather vane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silky, long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A firm, slim waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms as long as a giraffe's neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there other good qualities?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slender legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More good qualities!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voluptuous E-cups!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White skin, the colour of tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're iterating your merits, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did their conversation end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pores that you'd need a microscope to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A face as small as a water flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really focusing on the exterior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like them to mention some inner values too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.00,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Outstanding sense of style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan only likes to praise Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pitiful... getting annoyed and trying to get sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous, you have your own merits, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There's s-small breasts fetish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slender is in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the strike zone for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if she has a nice figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan is like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal this summer is to lose 3 kilograms and attain a figure befitting of a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about true summer, then you mean August.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer hasn't even started yet for high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another month...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In another month, I can make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer starts today for high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing into our swimsuits just to clean the pool is such a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But cleaning in a swimsuit sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you think so too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I gained weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think these swimsuits shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a lot of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The swimsuit shrank!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Nagi acting weird today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her usual self, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yutaka's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm also a fan of yours, like Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had the chance to ask, but I've been wondering about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this natural, or do you do something to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mipo-rin, that's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering Toorun yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not clinging to her like you do, Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you get all the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna touch her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just... {TLC}{just went with something that seemed a little more natural, since it's only "An(a)ta ne..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you two seem close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go to the same middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though it's a bit unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She keeps looking at her watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, 3 minutes have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off Tooru-san right now, Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mipo-rin, you're cold-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it, so if Yutaka bothers you, tell me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During middle school, her nickname was "Remote."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that's totally lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the origin of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.15,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've really wanted to touch Tooru's hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.94,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}[Trash bag]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san, I'll hold that trash bag for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mipo-rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.46,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Remote...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun... shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poolside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it feel like a resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere to escape from the heat of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, Nagi-chan, it's really slippery here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you fall and hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you tell her too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dripping wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... If that's how you want to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.70,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.70,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.24,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fscx90}There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not paradise at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:56.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\c&H175BEC&\bord18\pos(994.5,399)\3c&HD4D8CD&}Had to stay behind \Nsince they didn't finish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:56.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\c&H175BEC&\bord15\pos(994.5,399)\3c&HF4FEFC&}Had to stay behind \Nsince they didn't finish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably should have put on more sunscreen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I worked my ass off all day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I've lost weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I've reached my goal of losing 3 kilos already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I want, scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, it's fine because I can subtract the 1 kilo that my clothes weigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that, my weight hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost to my nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:11.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\frz358.171\pos(1170,322.5)\c&HF8D964&\bord2.25\3c&HB6AC92&}Ba{\alpha&HFF}sics of Dieting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:11.47,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\frz358.171\pos(1170,322.5)\c&HF8D964&\bord2.25\3c&HB6AC92&}Basics of {\alpha&HFF}Dieting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:11.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\frz358.171\pos(1170,322.5)\c&HF8D964&\bord2.25\3c&HB6AC92&}Basics of Dieti{\alpha&HFF}ng
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.23,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\frz358.171\pos(1170,322.5)\c&HF8D964&\bord2.25\3c&HB6AC92&}Basics of Dieting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, form a one month plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the foundations are limited food intake and exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No snacking between meals."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A light, early dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Use mostly vegetables and non-greasy foods."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Keep exercising every day."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Exercises such as jogging, skipping and stretching are effective."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadistic, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep the fact that I'm dieting a secret from everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd just whine about it anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Run knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! It's bad for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine the way you are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... They would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious! Delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some? Take as much as you like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it makes me want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without meaning to, I jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru is really perceptive... I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're on a diet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Run and Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was dieting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in spring, you said that you were going to lose 3 kilos before summer, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered that yesterday, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Can't you just forget about stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want money to keep quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you eat loads of candy, you're really thin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I run around all the time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, there's isn't enough nutrition getting in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard they shrink if they shake too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can't skip or jog, solely because I'll lose my breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that worried about it, why not ask Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could've been working really hard to get what she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a secret to her figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we miss each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, you're sweating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are tears of sadness, because I can't see Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sweaty because we've been walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's already summer and you're still wearing long sleeves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to show my arms if I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're this unwilling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's all open the textbook to page 52.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? If I do something to maintain my figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really don't mean anything by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hold back on the things I like and I sleep a lot, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do anything, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of model are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no help at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining your figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about dieting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were talking about dieting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you start one, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to hide it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried a diet, Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not properly, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to limit what I can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have you, Yuuko-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, you keep a pet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pet? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a name like a surname...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tapeworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:08.10,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Sanadamushi is Japanese for tapeworm and also sounds similar to a surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the power of the tapeworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't keep one, and that's not a pet either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you search on the internet, I'm sure you'll find a good diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we come all the way to the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've used the one in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Researching this on the PC in the classroom is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of different diets, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"After I used this, I lost 60kg", it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lost that much, your weight would be negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be able to float!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ghost would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling what you eat is one of the basics of dieting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend you didn't hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible, because I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really get hungry around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad for your health if you start dieting all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start off more slowly, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just make it your goal for next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it at my own pace, without rushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange, with this flow of conversation, to suddenly move to ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want chocolate chip and strawberry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanilla, cheese and yoghurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all white!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:22.65,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll take mint and raspberry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rum raisin.
